  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Independent Interim Reviews and Final Evaluation of Rwanda Climate Change and Environment Fund (FONERWA) support projects</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The Environment and Climate Change Fund in Rwanda (FONERWA) has been operational since 2012. It was established by the Government of Rwanda with a view to it becoming Rwanda&#x2019;s primary vehicle through which environment and climate change finance is channelled, programmed, disbursed and monitored.

DFID has contracted Upper Quartile to conduct a final evaluation of a) the FONERWA Fund Management support model and b) an interim review and final evaluation of DFID&#x2019;s financing of FONERWA for climate change and environment projects.</narrative>
  </description>
